# DocumentObservation.Container.List.Item

**Structure**

A single element of a list.

## Declaration

```swift
struct Item
```

## Inspecting an item

- **content**: The content of the list item.
- **itemString**: The transcript of the list item, excluding the list marker.
- **markerString**: The list marker as a string.
- **markerType**: The style of the list marker.
